snippet.title: Meta Meet Cute!!!+ Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
The official trailer of Meta Meet Cute!!!+.
Join the chaos of love and avoid the pitfalls of passion in the New Visual Novel Meta Meet Cute!!!+ coming to Nintendo February 14th!
